’Щ@9176b13a6b64826918a6f3e013f170b0918d25211f2305b9114a41abe9560d80ЪҜTitle: title: date list-timezone
Path: Examples
Content:
Show time zone(s) that contains 'Shanghai'.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date list-timezone | where timezone =~ Shanghai
